{"type": "article", "id": 22384, "title": "故意露出缝线的沙发", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-17T07:30:12Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 23, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606160051BGLdSe6VNsotlPgR.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是由夫妻档组合 FÄRG &amp; BLANCHE 设计的扶手椅，他们开发了一种“wood tailoring”技术，即木材缝纫的技术。扶手椅的硬木外壳和布料软垫是通过缝线的方式钉在一起，黑色的线条很明显地出现在浅色的木材上，有种特别的手工感。此外，沙发的扶手和靠背都是一个模块，是用拼接的方式衔接起来的，有助于回收材料。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061600490V48BnzcuqIZvXMW.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.7200489\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160049MTouVnFE7mh8GOz1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74938875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160050dEmkzQn8ITrvsAPK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74938875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061600506cEsnkKHGbyYflQa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.18215159\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n\n"}